<doc id="907281" wikidata="Q609897" url="?curid=907281" title="Antti Viitikko">
<text>Antti Viitikko (born 29 November 1976 in Espoo) is a male badminton player from Finland. Viitikko played badminton at the 2004 Summer Olympics in men&#x27;s singles, losing in the round of 32 to Shon Seung-mo of Korea.

