==In popular culture==
In December 2017, the first trailer for his biopic movie was released. Entitled &quot;Lee Chong Wei&quot;, the biopic premiered on 9 March 2018 at the Bukit Jalil National Stadium, Kuala Lumpur, and was released nationwide on 15 March 2018.

